        </tei:address><tei:lb/>
        <tei:salute rend="indent-20"><tei:handShift new="SG"/>My dearest <tei:rs type="person"
            key="entity-000771">Lilli</tei:rs>,<tei:ptr corresp="#r0001-fn01" type="footnote"
          /></tei:salute>
      </tei:opener>

      <tei:p>At long last I can reply to your dear letter.<tei:ptr corresp="#r0001-fn02"
          type="footnote"/> We have had several weeks here that were quite alarming. Thank God that
        I can at last write to you. – How gladly my children<tei:ptr corresp="#r0001-fn03"
          type="footnote"/> would like to help your son<tei:ptr corresp="#r0001-fn04"
          type="footnote"/>; my dear <tei:rs type="person" key="entity-000317">Julko</tei:rs> has
        rescued several people entirely unknown to him. – But <tei:hi rend="underline">now</tei:hi>
        it is out of the question. – No one can get hold of an entry permit here. – – – not for love
        nor money. – Perhaps the time will come? At the moment, it is not possible to do it. With
        the best will, I can't say anything more to you than that. – – –</tei:p>

      <tei:p><tei:pb n="2"/> At the wish of our children, we will be moving to <tei:rs type="place"
          key="entity-002375">Czernowitz</tei:rs> in November, so that we are no longer nest-sitting
        so alone. – Now it is a matter of finding a house, moving, and building a home again on the
        basis of the old days. But our nerves are already in tatters from this news coming out of
        the small towns – – – So we will have our charming little girls<tei:ptr
          corresp="#r0001-fn05" type="footnote"/> close to us and be among <tei:supplied
          reason="clarity">good</tei:supplied> people. God give me peace!! –</tei:p>

      <tei:p>So, my dearest, I assure you by all that is holy that if only it were possible your
        wish would be fulfilled immediately. Perhaps a new day will come?? I have just been with my
        children for a few days: what I saw there – – – I can't go on any longer: <tei:rs
          type="person" key="entity-003932">Oskar</tei:rs> has arrived and I will send the letter
        off. </tei:p>

      <tei:closer>
        <tei:salute rend="indent-40">With many heartfelt greetings,</tei:salute>
        <tei:salute rend="indent-40">I remain your faithful</tei:salute>
        <tei:signed rend="indent-70"><tei:rs type="person" key="entity-000319"
          >Sophie</tei:rs></tei:signed><tei:lb/>
